OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fgradually fading overnight and then
OL,7,Fmainly dry but rather cloudy, though
OL,8,Frain reaching the Northern Isles by
OL,9,Fdawn. Chilly in the north with patchy
OL,10,Frural frost; milder further south.
