OL,12,CMonday:FRain slowly moving across
OL,13,Fnorthern Scotland. Rather cloudy for
OL,14,Fcentral and southern areas with
OL,15,Foccasional showers, heavy in the
OL,16,Fsouthwest. Mostly dry elsewhere with
OL,17,Fsome sunny spells.
